info.author: Ondrej Palkovsky
info.description:
Yet another Object-relational mapping. It supports PosgreSQL and makes creating
dynamic queries a piece of cake. No schema description in python is necessary.
supports inner and outer joins, aggreagte functions with automatic grouping,
transformation of python function to SQL case statement.
